lead_paragraph: Everton's 5-0 drubbing by an inspired and ruthless Chelsea team at Stamford Bridge on Saturday left midfielder Tom Cleverley feeling embarrassed.

headline.print_headline: Everton Embarrassed by Chelsea Rout, Says Cleverley
